  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and saute for 1 minute.",
    "Add the Korean chili flakes and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the vegetable broth, soy sauce, and Korean dumpling noodles, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the lettuce leaves to the pot and cook until wilted.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with green onions and toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Serve the sujebi hot, with the noodles and lettuce in a bowl and the broth on the side."
